</span></h2><p class="sc-jHkVzv jQDaRw pf-20_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fIosxK dnoTqD pf-22_">In over two decades of working in the health and social care sector, I have witnessed numerous challenges, but none as critical as what we face today in England. The adult social care sector, an integral part of our society's fabric, stands at a crucial crossroads.<br><br>This blog delves into the multi-dimensional crisis engulfing the sector, reflecting on the voices of those at its heart and exploring avenues for urgent reform.
</span></p><h1 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-eLwHnm eiMYhK pf-23_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fIosxK dnoTqD pf-25_">The unfolding crisis
