</b>
</span></h1><p class="sc-jHkVzv jQDaRw pf-33_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fIosxK dnoTqD pf-35_">The COVID-19 pandemic has not only highlighted but also exacerbated the chronic staffing shortages in the sector. These shortages have been compounded by inadequate support and remuneration, leading to burnout and attrition.
