</span></h1><p class="sc-jHkVzv jQDaRw pf-39_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fIosxK dnoTqD pf-41_">Frequent changes in political leadership have led to inconsistent policymaking, creating uncertainty and instability, which undermines long-term strategic planning and investment in the sector.
</span></p><h1 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-eLwHnm eiMYhK pf-42_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fIosxK dnoTqD pf-44_"><b>Funding gaps</b>
